nodes.text: Onie Arkmen was a human female living on Coruscant during the last decades of the Galactic Republic. She was present in the Outlander Club when Anakin Skywalker and Obi-Wan Kenobi were seeking Zam Wesell. A partygoer, Arkmen was scarcely dressed with small silver shorts, a small chain-mail top, and golden high heels, and wore an elaborate hairstyle and dark makeup.
